PM3BAUD.original: ~z~They're after us, boys. Check the other platform.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~他们还在追我们，小子们。注意另一个站台。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Alright, we make a move around the back. Follow me.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Alright, we make a move around the back. Follow me.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Niko, that thing can't take all of us and this cash. Use your head, man.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Niko, that thing can't take all of us and this cash. Use your head, man.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Check to the right for us, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Check to the right for us, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~That's a fucking sea of blue. Get in cover, boys!
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~That's a fucking sea of blue. Get in cover, boys!

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Get us a car will you, Niko?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Get us a car will you, Niko?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Get down, we don't wanna hurt civilians.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Get down, we don't wanna hurt civilians.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Come on, think of the money, people.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Come on, think of the money, people.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You ain't invincible, Niko. Get in cover.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You ain't invincible, Niko. Get in cover.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Alright, boys. The only way we got to go is along the tracks. Come on.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~好了小子们。我们唯一的去路就是顺着轨道走了。来吧。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Sure you do, you believe in the needle and its power to make the rest of the world disappear, while you dream of nonsense.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Sure you do, you believe in the needle and its power to make the rest of the world disappear, while you dream of nonsense.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You did it, let's bust out of here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You did it, let's bust out of here.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Can you get us some transport, Niko?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Can you get us some transport, Niko?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, just staying here ain't going to work. There are too many of them.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Shit, just staying here ain't going to work. There are too many of them.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~How is you, me and Derrick gonna fit in there with the money?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~How is you, me and Derrick gonna fit in there with the money?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Another fucking truck full of 'em. They're blocking us in.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Another fucking truck full of 'em. They're blocking us in.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I ain't going to jail in this country.
~z~We ain't doing that neither. Follow me. We'll lose them in the subway.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~不用这么做。跟我来，进地铁站甩掉他们。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Niko, you gotta hang in there. Don't die on us.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Niko, you gotta hang in there. Don't die on us.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I got plans for this money. I ain't dropping it.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~我都想好这钱咋花了，我是不会放弃的。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We ain't got no choice, people. We gotta head onto the track.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~我们没别的选择了，各位。只能走铁轨了。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~This ain't the type of thing I agree with. I ain't in it for the money. I believe in something, you know?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~This ain't the type of thing I agree with. I ain't in it for the money. I believe in something, you know?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Okay, boys. We're outta here. Follow me round the back.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Okay, boys. We're outta here. Follow me round the back.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, this door's locked. Shoot the lock, Niko. We got you covered.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Shit, this door's locked. Shoot the lock, Niko. We got you covered.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I ain't built for being underground like this.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I ain't built for being underground like this.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Both of you shut the fuck up.
~z~More cops are joining in the party, boys.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~更多的警察加入派对了，小子们。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We don't want another casualty on this job. Hang in there, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~We don't want another casualty on this job. Hang in there, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Jesus, they're blocking off the damn road. There's another truck full of those bastards.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Jesus, they're blocking off the damn road. There's another truck full of those bastards.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Chinatown always smells like Chinatown no matter where you are or how much gun powder is in the air.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~火药打得再多，唐人街还是一股唐人街的味儿。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~This ain't working. We need to get out of here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~This ain't working. We need to get out of here.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Give us some cover while we run for the subway, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Give us some cover while we run for the subway, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We just made a withdrawal, what's the problem?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~我们不过是要撤退而已，搞什么啊？

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~And you coulda been more careful of your boy Michael. He should be with us right now.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~你咋不多护着点你手下的Michael，~n~否则他哪会没命啊。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I got told this was going to be a smooth job. Real easy, they told me. No casualties.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I got told this was going to be a smooth job. Real easy, they told me. No casualties.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Go back home to your kids. You don't wanna die here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~回家带孩子去吧。你们不会想死在这儿的。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Jesus, Niko. You look like death. Come on.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Jesus, Niko. You look like death. Come on.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~This'll all be worth it when we're back at Ma's with the cash.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~This'll all be worth it when we're back at Ma's with the cash.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Cover us while we make a run for it, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Cover us while we make a run for it, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Both of you shut up. You're behaving like children.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Both of you shut up. You're behaving like children.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I saw your eyes light up when you thought about all the drugs you could buy with this haul.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I saw your eyes light up when you thought about all the drugs you could buy with this haul.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Great, we're free from this fucking dungeon. Let's go.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Great, we're free from this fucking dungeon. Let's go.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Let's bring this fucker down. Empty everything we got into him.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~把这个狗逼打下来。射光手头的弹药。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You coulda mixed the explosive better couldn't ya, Derrick?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~炸弹你可以弄得更好点的吧，Derrick？

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Just what we needed, boys. More fucking cops.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~真是时候，小子们。又他妈一群条子。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~This is typical. A typical fucking McReary family screw up. Can't we do nothing right.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~This is typical. A typical fucking McReary family screw up. Can't we do nothing right.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You've been beat up good, Niko. Pull through, okay?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You've been beat up good, Niko. Pull through, okay?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~They've sent in another fucking van, boys.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~They've sent in another fucking van, boys.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Jesus, Packie. Show some fucking consideration. Sorry if I'm a man of principle unlike you and Gerald.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Jesus, Packie. Show some fucking consideration. Sorry if I'm a man of principle unlike you and Gerald.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Up, up, up. Come on, let's go.
~z~Get in cover, Packie. Ma'd be real upset if you got hit.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Get in cover, Packie. Ma'd be real upset if you got hit.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Will ya look left for us, Niko?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Will ya look left for us, Niko?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Fuck, boys. I ain't doing too good over here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Fuck, boys. I ain't doing too good over here.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We got some climbing to do, boys. Hold onto your money.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~我们要往上爬了，小子们。把钱拿住喽。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Looks like we got more N.O.O.S.E. to deal with, people.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Looks like we got more N.O.O.S.E. to deal with, people.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You ain't looking too good, Niko. Hang in there.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You ain't looking too good, Niko. Hang in there.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~There's light at the end of the tunnel, boys. We're nearly there.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~There's light at the end of the tunnel, boys. We're nearly there.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~He's going to love the fact that us boys pulled off the biggest bank heist in this city's history.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~He's going to love the fact that us boys pulled off the biggest bank heist in this city's history.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I never shoulda come back to Liberty City. I knew Gerald would get me back into this shit.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I never shoulda come back to Liberty City. I knew Gerald would get me back into this shit.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Niko, make sure we're not being fucked from behind.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Niko, make sure we're not being fucked from behind.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Packie, get in cover before you get yourself killed.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Packie, get in cover before you get yourself killed.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Hurry up and shoot the fucking lock, will you?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Hurry up and shoot the fucking lock, will you?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Niko, will ya keep an eye to the left?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Niko, will ya keep an eye to the left?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We got cops coming up behind us. Shit.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~We got cops coming up behind us. Shit.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~There ain't no way round these fucks, we're going through 'em.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~There ain't no way round these fucks, we're going through 'em.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, they sent a chopper after us. There ain't no getting away. We're done.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~操，他们派出直升机了。这下逃不掉了，我们完了。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I feel like I'm in a fucking tomb.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I feel like I'm in a fucking tomb.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~There's a fucking train coming. Watch out.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~There's a fucking train coming. Watch out.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Keep an eye to the rear, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Keep an eye to the rear, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Fuck, the door's locked. Shoot the lock out, Niko. We'll cover you.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Fuck, the door's locked. Shoot the lock out, Niko. We'll cover you.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~The fucking train is running us down. Christ.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~The fucking train is running us down. Christ.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna knock myself out for the fucking count. Try to forget about all this shit.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I'm gonna knock myself out for the fucking count. Try to forget about all this shit.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~That's gotta be a service exit. Let's hit it.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~那个应该是维护出口，走那儿吧。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, I don't wanna die down here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Shit, I don't wanna die down here.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~These cops is gonna fucking trap us in this tunnel. Shit!
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~这群条子想把我们困在隧道里，操！

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You don't want to get in my way.
~z~I can taste the fresh air, boys. Can't have long to go.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I can taste the fresh air, boys. Can't have long to go.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I need you to clear the area for us, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I need you to clear the area for us, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko. Check in front of us.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Shit, Niko. Check in front of us.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You're doing fucking great, boys. Let's get up these stairs.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~你们都他妈干得很好，小子们。赶紧上楼吧。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We can't let these cops pin us down in here. Fuck!
~z~Watch out, Packie. Get in some cover.
~z~Control yourself, Derrick. I got a plan.
~z~They ain't gonna get us from behind, boys. I got it covered.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~They ain't gonna get us from behind, boys. I got it covered.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Looks like we got a whole precinct worth a cops out here. Get in some cover.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Looks like we got a whole precinct worth a cops out here. Get in some cover.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You don't wanna stand in our fucking way.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You don't wanna stand in our fucking way.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I ain't been here since Frankie threw me a farewell dinner when I was going to Ireland. That was a lifetime ago.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~上次来这儿还是去爱尔兰之前，Frankie为我饯行的时候。已经是很久以前了。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Don't stand in our way because we don't want to hurt you.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Don't stand in our way because we don't want to hurt you.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna give myself a double dose when I get home.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I'm gonna give myself a double dose when I get home.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Stick to the tracks, Niko. Come on.
~z~I could do with some chop right now!
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I could do with some chop right now!

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Fucking get rid of these guys, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Fucking get rid of these guys, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Our argument's with the police, not innocent civilians. Get down.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Our argument's with the police, not innocent civilians. Get down.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Niko you're the getaway driver. Will ya get us back to my ma's?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Niko you're the getaway driver. Will ya get us back to my ma's?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You almost lost me and a big bag of money there, boys.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~你们刚才差点就要没了我和一大包钱，小子们。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Let's charge through these fucks, people. There ain't no time for second thoughts.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Let's charge through these fucks, people. There ain't no time for second thoughts.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Watch the bags, boys. We don't want holes in our notes.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~包当心点，小子们。大家都不想钞票上长眼儿。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~If this was easy then everyone would rob banks.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~If this was easy then everyone would rob banks.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko. Will you handle these boys?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Shit, Niko. Will you handle these boys?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~There ain't no reason to get in my way.
~z~Shit, that was closer than I'm comfortable with.
~z~We're gonna head right, okay? Move it.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~We're gonna head right, okay? Move it.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We'll be laughing about this shit tomorrow, boys, I promise ya that.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~We'll be laughing about this shit tomorrow, boys, I promise ya that.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Alright, Niko. Take us back to my ma's, will ya?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Alright, Niko. Take us back to my ma's, will ya?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Ain't no one coming at us from the right, people.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Ain't no one coming at us from the right, people.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~The train's heading right for us. Watch yourselves.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~The train's heading right for us. Watch yourselves.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~That's gotta be a way outta here, boys. Come on.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~那边应该有路出去，小子们。来吧。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~There are too many of them, we'll die if we stay here.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~There are too many of them, we'll die if we stay here.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~This ain't my idea of fun, boys. Would ya give me a hand?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~This ain't my idea of fun, boys. Would ya give me a hand?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Shit, they've followed us down here. They're in the subway too.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~操，他们跟到这儿来了，地铁站里也是他们的人。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Make sure these pricks don't shoot the bags. Notes with bullet holes in 'em are gonna be mighty hard to get rid of.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~别让这些屌人打到包上面。有弹孔的钱可花不出去。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You don't wanna die for the bank's cash.
~z~Shit, you don't never know what you're dealing with when you're in Chinatown.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~操，你永远不会知道你在唐人街干的是谁的。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You knew what this job was when you signed up. Don't pretend that you're all holier than thou.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You knew what this job was when you signed up. Don't pretend that you're all holier than thou.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~I ain't gonna be around much longer at this rate. Fucking help me!
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~I ain't gonna be around much longer at this rate. Fucking help me!

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Alright man, get these guys, will ya?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Alright man, get these guys, will ya?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~The cops is down here too. Check over there, boys.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~下面也有条子。进去小心点，小子们。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Michael was unlucky. It wasn't anybody's fault what happened to him and the explosive did its job.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Michael运气差了点。~n~他出事怪不了谁，炸弹也够好了。

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~You're right. Let's cut around the back. Follow my lead.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~You're right. Let's cut around the back. Follow my lead.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Don't be fucking stupid, get in cover, Niko.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Don't be fucking stupid, get in cover, Niko.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Everybody get down. We don't want no one hurt who don't gotta be.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Everybody get down. We don't want no one hurt who don't gotta be.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~We got more cops on us, people.
~z~Don't get this money shot up, boys.
~z~Okay, we're making a right up here. Come on.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Okay, we're making a right up here. Come on.

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~Will you shoot the fucking lock already, Niko?
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~Will you shoot the fucking lock already, Niko?

PM3BAUD.original: ~z~The can't be another truck full of them. Jesus. They're blocking the roads.
PM3BAUD.translated: ~z~The can't be another truck full of them. Jesus. They're blocking the roads.
